headline: Here’s Why Oakmark Equity and Income Fund Added Molina Healthcare (MOH) to its Portfolio
summary: Oakmark Funds, advised by Harris Associates, released its “Oakmark Equity and Income Fund” Q1 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund’s investor class delivered 0.91% during the quarter compared to -1.45% returns for the 60% S&P 500 / 40% Bloomberg U.S. Aggregate Bond Index. The equity portfolio returned -0.25% […]
